  2   * @file main.c
  3   * @brief ILI9488 Color Fill Demo
  4   *
  5   * Cycles through solid colors on a 320x480 ILI9488 display connected to a Raspberry Pi 4B via SPI0:
  6   *   SPI device : /dev/spidev0.0  (10 MHz)
  7   *   RESET GPIO : BCM 24 (Pin 18)
  8   *   D/C GPIO   : BCM 25 (Pin 22)
  9   *   CS         : BCM  8 / SPI0_CE0 (Pin 24) -- handled by spidev
 10   *
 11   * AI Usage Disclaimer: This file was mostly outlined then generated using AI tools. See ./AI_chats for the full conversation logs as best as could be exported.
